{{Otheruses|Grappler}}
The '''Grappler''' was an organic ship created by the living [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]] during the [[Battle of Yuuzhan'tar]] as part of the "Fight Without Fighting" plan against the [[Yuuzhan Vong]].<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

They resembled a [[maidenfly]] insect with green wings and red carapaces. They also had a grasping hand and [[dovin basal]]-like [[Gravity/Legends|gravity]] projectors to bring down [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] fighters and Yuuzhan Vong [[Alpha Red (pathogen)|Alpha Red]]-infected [[Yorik-et|coralskippers]].<ref name="TUF" />

